{"tid":817261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【iP XS殺到】台灣售價比港日貴！網友怨：能買電單車了","createTime":"2018-09-13T09:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T11:19:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bd572eb9d4580c3243698d81c58a0b0d411df8e8","tid":817261,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T09:17:20.000Z","msg":"5,521<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0913 11:35<br />\n <br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n蘋果今日發佈3款新iPhone，台灣列入首波開賣地區，最高規格的iPhone Xs Max 512GB售價52,900元新台幣(下同、13,488港元)，價格一公佈討論熱度隨即壓過新機功能，無論果粉或卓粉對於破5萬天價都嚇到呆。<br />\n<br />\n專門提供台日航線廉價航空比價的網站「<a href=\"http://Just.崩潰.ME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FJust.%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0.ME&d=XXdYi8UEbcfAy5bMgVLqrb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=8a80da62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Just.崩潰.ME</a>」，立刻製表比拼台灣、香港、日本3地的iPhone新機價格，台灣3款新機售價都比香港、日本還高，價差最多的就是頂規iPhone Xs Max 512GB版本，已被稱為「史上最貴iPhone」，然而台灣售價又硬生生比日本未稅價多了6464元(1,648港元)，即使是用日本含稅價來計算，台灣還是貴了2747元(700港元)；與香港相比，台灣依然最貴，高出3054元(778港元)。<br />\n<br />\n而在中國iPhone XS Max 512GB港版賣$12,499人民幣(下同)，中國版折合$14,655，大概貴$2,156；iPhone XR 256G港版賣$7,799，中國版折合$9,044，大概貴$1,245。 <br />\n<br />\n比價表引發台灣網友抱怨又被當盤子，紛紛哀號：「這定價根本是逼人跳槽」、「5萬都能買摩托車了」、「52K買Macbook就好了吧」、「蘋果重新定義了台幣的價值」、「今年不買明年更貴」。<br />\n<br />\n日本未稅價雖然較台灣售價便宜許多，但是日本當地能退稅的都是較大型的電器賣場或是可退稅的商家，蘋果新機在這些地方並不容易買到，要利用退稅與匯差撿便宜，沒有想像中容易；另外要注意的是，因為日本變態偷拍猖獗，日本的手機都會強制開啟相機快門聲，就連iPhone切換到靜音模式也無法關閉快門聲，想偷拍、自拍的情境下會很尷尬。"},{"pid":"44fd9f2ead5a40efd2793f67c9399b339a5445cf","tid":817261,"uid":41368,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T09:22:26.000Z","msg":"蘋果都唔想啲台狗窮撚用部機"},{"pid":"30b57b2cd6f0ea2da58d330349b51025335bbceb","tid":817261,"uid":10433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"仲多過台灣仔一個月人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d0980858e45124fbf82b6ac66b8bd25277f740","tid":817261,"uid":39628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T09:31:30.000Z","msg":"怨乜鬼<br />\n又唔係用槍指住你買<br />\n無錢又要用, 咪買最平個部lor"},{"pid":"ff3cc0f05c8bcf6e7538f38228161a704f2ea523","tid":817261,"uid":58609,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"30b57b2cd6f0ea2da58d330349b51025335bbceb","tid":817261,"uid":10433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"仲多過台灣仔一個月人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T09:33:44.000Z","msg":"一萬二都係唔少hk fg人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f86252b6676a1b300bd5a8f945e68fff90c180a4","tid":817261,"uid":45368,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"30b57b2cd6f0ea2da58d330349b51025335bbceb","tid":817261,"uid":10433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T09:25:27.000Z","msg":"仲多過台灣仔一個月人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T09:45:26.000Z","msg":"點止一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b807a10da07b83e908e3a34440a2f14df5bec071","tid":817261,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T09:57:34.000Z","msg":"台妹想唔想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068aa4be20aa0440131d7ac9915943b27bf54236","tid":817261,"uid":182638,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T09:58:45.000Z","msg":"拎住部iPhone去搶台狗啲女先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c4c6d8e9d046653f01f09dd9a6421aea5b7710e","tid":817261,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T09:58:55.000Z","msg":"係咪可以拎iphone去台灣揾台妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94cbd81bbbd217837ed024f14104de09a787d608","tid":817261,"uid":182638,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2